data.description: Great opportunity to affordably own your home or build your investment portfolio. Here is a solid 2 bed, 1 bath brick home with a full basement that is partially finished. Potentially double the square footage of this home by finishing out the basement. 2 car detached garage and gated yard. Basement is partially finished (good ceiling height) and is ready for your ideas. The home has central heat & AC, laundry facilities in the basement, fenced in back yard.  Hardwood throughout, even under the carpets in the bedrooms. Home needs some TLC but is ready to go. Don't let this opportunity pass by.
